title: Natural Tucker Cafe and Health Foods
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Macrobiotic, Organic, Western, Fast food, Juice bar, Take-out
description: Cafe and health food shop. Food menu includes aduki bean and kumera, tempeh, lentil, tofu or falafel patties in a burger, pita wrap or sandwich, veggie pies and rolls, and more. Fresh juice, tea and coffee. Also sells various snacks in the connected organic health food store including many vegan and gluten free options. Confirmed open Feb 2011.
